; Coverage for report.cc commodities_report limit conjunction
; When commodities_report strips state predicates from a compound limit,
; if 2+ non-state terms remain, they are re-joined with &
; Here --cleared is a state predicate (stripped), while the two --limit
; expressions survive and get conjoined: (total>0)&(commodity=~/AAPL/).

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00
P 2024/01/01 GOOG $100.00
P 2024/01/01 MSFT $200.00

2024/01/01 * Buy
    Assets:Stocks    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Stocks    5 GOOG @ $100.00
    Assets:Stocks    3 MSFT @ $200.00
    Assets:Cash

test commodities --cleared --limit 'total>0' --limit 'commodity=~/AAPL/'
$
AAPL
end test
